  </Products>
</STEP-ProductInformation>


### 10e — Verify: list changes for DIM-PRODUCT-001 and assert qualifier breakdown
# Run after 10a–10d.  Expected change log:
#   From 10a (baseline): 13 records  — all qualifiers as new values
#   From 10b (partial):   4 records  — en, de, CZ10, USD only
#   From 10c (new ja):    1 record   — ja only
#   From 10d (no-op):     0 records
# Total: 18 ChangeRecords for DIM-PRODUCT-001
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/changes?step_product_id=DIM-PRODUCT-001&page=1&page_size=50
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10e-i — Filter to only locale-dimension changes (MarketingDescription)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/changes?step_product_id=DIM-PRODUCT-001&attribute_id=MarketingDescription&page=1&page_size=50
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10e-ii — Filter to a single qualifier (CZ10 market context)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/changes?step_product_id=DIM-PRODUCT-001&qualifier_id=CZ10&page=1&page_size=50
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10e-iii — Filter to unit dimension changes (ListPrice)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/changes?step_product_id=DIM-PRODUCT-001&attribute_id=ListPrice&page=1&page_size=50
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
